title: Offseason Clickbait, Foles Future, Free Agent Market, Cousins' Destination (Football 02/20)
description:
Will Brinson, Pete Prisco and Jason La Canfora get together for an offseason edition of the Pick Six podcast. Pete addresses Tony Dungy's Tweets towards him and defends his take on Nick Foles. The guys also discuss the Bucs offseason plans, the free agent market, Kirk Cousins possibilities, and early Mock Drafts!
